    "title": "Senior Software Engineer - Mphasis - Freshers Welcome",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Senior Software Engineer looking for your next big career move? Mphasis in Srinagar offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Mphasis:\nMphasis is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Learning & development budget\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mphasis!",
